=====安全=====
2017年5月，Countryman在歐洲[[EuroNCAP|Euro NCAP]]撞擊測試獲得最高級別的五星評級，當中包括了車內成年乘客的保護度達90%，兒童乘客保護度達83%，當中還有多項測試取得高分。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.euroncap.com/en/results/mini/countryman/26807 |title=MINI Countryman 2017 granted 5-star crash rating |publisher=euroncap.com |access-date=2018-10-08 |archive-date=2020-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201025113306/https://www.euroncap.com/en/results/mini/countryman/26807 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

